{"word":"ἀφθονία","slug":"ἀφθονία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφθονία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:φθονέω'><el>φθονέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>freedom from envy</i> or <i>grudging, readiness</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>plenty, abundance</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}